summary: This is an email exchange regarding the transmission of Jeffrey Epstein's passport photos. The FBI New York - C20 Human Trafficking team confirms receipt of nine photos sent via multiple emails and asks for confirmation if more are expected.

persons.name: Jeffrey Epstein
persons.context: His passport photos are being transmitted between parties in this email exchange as part of an investigation.

events.title: Transmission of Epstein passport photos
events.description: The FBI New York - C20 Human Trafficking team confirms receipt of nine passport photos of Jeffrey Epstein sent via multiple emails.

keyFacts: The FBI New York - C20 Human Trafficking team was actively collecting Jeffrey Epstein's passport photos as of July 2019.
Nine passport photos of Epstein were transmitted via multiple emails due to file size constraints.
The email exchange shows coordination between parties regarding evidentiary materials in the Epstein investigation.
